      "briefTitle": "DORADO - Fixed Doses of Darusentan as Compared to Placebo in Resistant Hypertension",
      "officialTitle": "DORADO - A Phase 3, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Multi-Center, Parallel Group Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Fixed Doses of Darusentan in Subjects With Resistant Systolic Hypertension Receiving Combination Therapy With Three or More Antihypertensive Drugs, Including a Diuretic (Protocol DAR-311)"
